 whole effect of leveling past 60 effectively killed groupin in zones like velketors, old sebilis, the hole, etc.  Zones where one could got and kill things and get xp, now they are mostly empty as people spend 53-65 in Tier 1 zones... This would definitely help spread people out over the world instead of crowding them into tier 1 planes. <p><table>
