<br>
Mages CAN solo PoP mobs.  Yes, it is slower than grouping.  But seriously, what do you expect?  Wouldnt you think that killing tougher mobs (i.e. mobs you can only kill with a group) would yield more experience?  I don't know...it all makes sense to me.<br>
<br>
Yes, if you do want to solo, I do think you should go to Umbral Plains, or Innovation...or some other zone with mobs that you CAN kill.  YES the experience is slower. YES I do think it should be that way. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=106710"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/rhionsligo.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <br>
