<br>
I'm responding to a request to brainstorm solo-ability, in PoP.<br>
<br>
I'm fairly happy with the Mage role, as it exists today. <br>
<br>
However, our role with regard to soloing has changed trememdously, with regard to PoP.  I can understand frustration there, particularly as our old solo-brothers continue to solo extremely efficiently, and with an even greater reward than before.<br>
<br>
As to this particular thread, it's all pie-in-the-sky, anyway, but it's an interesting discussion, nevertheless.<br>
